Project name: Community Help Hup
Features:
1. Bulletin Board (Shows favours and requests)
2. Ranking system and match (points-based rank system)
3. Emergency alert
4. In-app messaging system
5. Verification
6. Report or flag
7. Task history and transfer
8. Dashboard
Project name: Multiplayer Quiz Game
Features:
1. Room creation and join
2. Timed multiple-choice questions
3. Leaderboard
4. Question management
5. Score history
6. Match analytics
7. Adaptive difficulty
8. Power up/ sabotage mechanics
